Amaze File Manager has been in active development for over *6 years* now.
We started with a goal to build a light weight, good looking, open source file manager for Android, since back in the day all three of these aspects were not present in Android ecosystem.
This somewhat holds true to this day. So we keep pushing with the same philosophy.

Amaze has been contributed by over *100 developers* throughout the world.
